OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRemaining dry with low cloud
OL,6,Faffecting coastal areas throughout the
OL,7,Fday. Plenty of sunshine to be had away
OL,8,Ffrom coasts. Temperatures around
OL,9,Faverage, cooler along the coast with
OL,10,Fan onshore breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA clear evening for many
OL,13,Fplaces inland. Overnight, low cloud
OL,14,Fmoves in from the North Sea. Remaining
OL,15,Fdry for most with a light
OL,16,Fnortheasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
