OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy start, but the
OL,6,Fcloud retreats to the coast through
OL,7,Fthe morning, leaving plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Temperatures near average,
OL,9,Fthough cooler along the coast with an
OL,10,Fonshore breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FGenerally cloudy mornings with
OL,14,Fbrighter afternoons to follow.
OL,15,FRemaining largely dry throughout.
OL,16,FBreezy at times, especially along the
OL,17,Fcoast. Temperatures around average or
OL,18,Fslightly above.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
